'''Abrahim Escudero Montoya''' (January 24, 1940 &ndash; November 6, 2009) was the [[Roman Catholic]] bishop of the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Palmira]], [[Colombia]].

Ordained on June 8, 1968, Escudero Montoya was named bishop on May 22, 1986, and he was ordained on June 21, 1986.<ref>http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bescmon.html</ref>

