oads/2016/07/ENG_PATRIARCHAL-CATHEDRAL-STAUROPIGIAL.pdf ''15 Century Bulgaria Foundation'' (15 века БЪЛГАРИЯ) website, article with title ''Patriarchal cathedral stauropigial memorial church St. Alexander Nevsky'' (pdf in English)]</ref> || [[Alexander Nevsky Cathedral, Sofia|Alexander Nevsky Cathedral]] || 1912 || [[Sofia]] || {{BUL}} || One of the [[List of largest Eastern Orthodox church buildings|largest Eastern Orthodox Cathedrals]] |}
